import React from 'react'
import { AddressCheckout, BagCheckout, Container, DotsCheckout, Logo, NavCheckOutSteps, NavContainer, NavLogo, NavSecure, PaymentCheckout, SecureLogo, SecureN } from './Cart.element'

const Cart = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
      <NavContainer>
        <NavLogo>
          <Logo src="https://images.indianexpress.com/2021/01/myntra.png" />
        </NavLogo>
        <NavCheckOutSteps>
          <BagCheckout>BAG</BagCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <AddressCheckout>ADDRESS</AddressCheckout>
          <DotsCheckout>---------</DotsCheckout>
          <PaymentCheckout>PAYMENT</PaymentCheckout>
        </NavCheckOutSteps>
        <NavSecure>
          <SecureLogo src="https://constant.myntassets.com/checkout/assets/img/sprite-secure.png" />
          <SecureN>100% SECURE</SecureN>
        </NavSecure>
      </NavContainer>
      <CartItems>
        <CartLeft></CartLeft>
      </CartItems>
    </Container>
  );
}

export default Cart
